      <title>Big Lots 申请破产，同意出售给 Nexus Capital</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-09/discount-retailer-big-lots-files-for-chapter-11-bankruptcy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[折扣零售商 Big Lots Inc. 已申请破产保护，并计划在法院监督下出售该公司的资产和正在进行的业务。]]></description>
